{"tid":2227383,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年第三季　App Store收益強勢增3成 達190億美金","createTime":"2020-10-02T17:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T02:15:13.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e101367b07534e17f56371c127874316b1f21b72","tid":2227383,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"據國際調研機構Sensor Tower最新統計出爐，兩大App平台美國蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)旗下App Store和Google旗下Google Play在2020年第三季，總計營收達到293億美元，且共有356億次的App下載量。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/XPVC3e6tB6OtAfOF45R7IUYujLA=/1376x942/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IQOVPQHWE5DSRFAIFPSVLRYMXQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXPVC3e6tB6OtAfOF45R7IUYujLA%3D%2F1376x942%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIQOVPQHWE5DSRFAIFPSVLRYMXQ.png&h=b7b975fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩大平台使用者花費增長比較。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/-WbGt3VIYBou5gtSNrgl1tPelwA=/1376x942/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SKJD2NYNLVAXZMC7PH6LZJS3KE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-WbGt3VIYBou5gtSNrgl1tPelwA%3D%2F1376x942%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSKJD2NYNLVAXZMC7PH6LZJS3KE.png&h=55392ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩大平台下載量增長比較。<br />\n<br />\n其中，App Store相比去年營收增長31%，下載量增加23.3%，在整體營收上達到190億美元，對照Google Play在2020年第三季營收的103億美元，幾乎多出一倍。<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是在365億的App下載量中，App Store僅佔了82億次，Google Play則高達283億次，反而是Google Play更多。App Store用戶的消費能力，顯然比Google Play用戶更高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報導另外附有2020第三季<br />\nApp下載量統計、生活應用App收益比較、手遊收益排名比較<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/gadget/20201003/X3GZBPDPCNDABBCFSLAGMRMPMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fgadget%2F20201003%2FX3GZBPDPCNDABBCFSLAGMRMPMA%2F&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=496572a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fgadget%2F20201003%2FX3GZBPDPCNDABBCFSLAGMRMPMA%2F&h=68a1ca4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/gadget/20201003/X3GZBPDPCNDABBCFSLAGMRMPMA/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://sensortower.com/blog/app-revenue-and-downloads-q3-2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsensortower.com%2Fblog%2Fapp-revenue-and-downloads-q3-2020&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=cf4f29f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://sensortower.com/blog/app-revenue-and-downloads-q3-2020</a>"},{"pid":"68e16df8836108b5a694057199b6e6c9263167eb","tid":2227383,"uid":209418,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T17:35:38.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩，股價都唔撚識升賺幾多都冇撚用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a199afc2aee5bc2a652cfd8ac6faf3fdda04fe","tid":2227383,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68e16df8836108b5a694057199b6e6c9263167eb","tid":2227383,"uid":209418,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T17:35:38.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩，股價都唔撚識升賺幾多都冇撚用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T17:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f34549010cde8f388c0709c07c0da57fd48c9d","tid":2227383,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T17:52:18.000Z","msg":"即係apple 好多錢但係落喺好少app度<br />\n以為好好賺但係根本無人會裝自己隻app"},{"pid":"ee21c392b33d130f57ed8b1e13c7b66f50984936","tid":2227383,"uid":203444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:55:30.000Z","msg":"遊戲App使用者花費方面，中國大廠騰訊有5款手遊入榜，其中Honor of Kings和PUBG Mobile為兩大榜單加總綜合營收最高的冠軍和亞軍。統計，收入最高的前5名手遊，總計占了24億美元營收。<br />\n姐係用apple既課金多，google 多免費仔<img src=\